milestones.description: Chumney and Codrington's 58-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 52 between Ashish Bagai and Ishwar Maraj
This is the lowest match aggregate (428) involving teams Netherlands & Canada in ODIs
Tim de Leede has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (20) for NED, going past Bas Zuiderent
